Definition: Name of the stream on which the prioritized crossings rests.
Priority in which measures should be taken for barrier remediation.
Owner of the crossing in question.
Quality of the modelled habitat upstream of the crossing. The habitat can vary due to a number of factors (e.g. slope)
Road name closest to the crossing in question.
Reason for which crossing should be remediated/ removed.
Extra information pertinent to the prioritzation of the crossing.
